articles.title: US sends 5 men to Eswatini under the Trump administration's deportation program - AP News
articles.description: The United States says it has sent five immigrants to the small African nation of Eswatini in an expansion of the Trump administration’s third-country deportation program. The U.S. already has deported eight men to another African nation, South Sudan, after t…
